"use strict";(self["webpackChunktome_planner"]=self["webpackChunktome_planner"]||[]).push([[6839],{26839:function(e){e.exports=JSON.parse('[{"__ATOMIC":true,"category":"uber","description":"Ultimate talents you may only know one.","hide":true,"name":"constitution","points":1,"source":"@vanilla@","talents":[{"cooldown":15,"id":"T_DRACONIC_BODY","image":"draconic_body.png","info_text":"<p>Your body hardens and recovers quickly. When pushed below 30% life, you instantly restore 40% of your total life.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Draconic Body","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Con 50; Be close to the draconic world"],"short_name":"DRACONIC_BODY","source_code":["data/talents/uber/const.lua",20],"type":["uber/constitution",1],"uber":true},{"cooldown":12,"id":"T_BLOODSPRING","image":"bloodspring.png","info_text":"<p>When a single blow deals more than 15% of your total life, a torrent of blood gushes from your body, creating a bloody tidal wave for 4 turns that deals <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Constitution 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">130, 175, 250, 325, 400</acronym> blight damage, heals you for 50% of the damage done, and knocks foes back.</p><p>The damage increases with your Constitution.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Bloodspring","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Con 50; Have let Melinda be sacrificed"],"short_name":"BLOODSPRING","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/uber/const.lua",38],"type":["uber/constitution",1],"uber":true},{"id":"T_ETERNAL_GUARD","image":"eternal_guard.png","info_text":"<p>Your Block talent now lasts for 2 game turns and you can apply Counterstrike to any number of enemies.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Eternal Guard","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Con 50; Know the Block talent"],"short_name":"ETERNAL_GUARD","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/uber/const.lua",67],"type":["uber/constitution",1],"uber":true},{"cooldown":8,"cost":"10 stamina","id":"T_NEVER_STOP_RUNNING","image":"never_stop_running.png","info_text":"<p>While this talent is active, you dig deep into your stamina reserves, allowing you to move without taking a turn. However, this costs 12 stamina for each tile that you cross.</p>","mode":"sustained","multi_require":false,"name":"Never Stop Running","no_energy":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 25, Con 50; Know at least 20 levels of stamina-using talents"],"short_name":"NEVER_STOP_RUNNING","source_code":["data/talents/uber/const.lua",77],"sustain_stamina":10,"type":["uber/constitution",1],"uber":true,"use_speed":"Instant"},{"id":"T_ARMOUR_OF_SHADOWS","image":"armour_of_shadows.png","info_text":"<p>You know how to protect yourself with the deepest shadows. As long as you stand on an unlit tile you gain <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Constitution 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">30, 30, 30, 37, 50</acronym> armour, 50% armour hardiness, and 20% evasion.</p><p>Any time you deal darkness damage, you will unlight both the target tile and yours.</p><p>Passively increases your stealth rating by 30.</p><p>The armor bonus scales with your Constitution.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Armour of Shadows","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Con 50; Have dealt over 50000 darkness damage"],"short_name":"ARMOUR_OF_SHADOWS","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/uber/const.lua",98],"type":["uber/constitution",1],"uber":true},{"id":"T_SPINE_OF_THE_WORLD","image":"spine_of_the_world.png","info_text":"<p>Your back is as hard as stone. Each time that you are affected by a physical effect, your body hardens, making you immune to all other physical effects for 5 turns.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Spine of the World","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Con 50"],"short_name":"SPINE_OF_THE_WORLD","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/uber/const.lua",122],"type":["uber/constitution",1],"uber":true},{"id":"T_FUNGAL_BLOOD","image":"fungal_blood.png","info_text":"<p>Fungal spores have colonized your blood, so that each time you use an infusion you store <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Constitution 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">25, 56, 107, 158, 209</acronym> fungal power.</p><p>You may use this prodigy to release the power as a heal (never more than <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Constitution 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">100, 138, 184, 220, 249</acronym> life) and remove up to 10 detrimental magical effects.</p><p>Fungal power lasts for up to 6 turns, losing the greater of 10 potency or 10% of its power each turn.</p><p>The amount of fungal power produced and the maximum heal possible increase with your Constitution and maximum life.</p>","mode":"activated","multi_require":false,"name":"Fungal Blood","no_energy":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 25, Con 50; Be able to use infusions"],"short_name":"FUNGAL_BLOOD","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/uber/const.lua",135],"type":["uber/constitution",1],"uber":true,"use_speed":"Instant"},{"id":"T_CORRUPTED_SHELL","image":"corrupted_shell.png","info_text":"<p>Thanks to your newfound knowledge of corruption, you\'ve learned some tricks for toughening your body&hellip; but only if you are healthy enough to withstand the strain from the changes.</p><p>Improves your life by 500, your defense by <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Constitution 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">3, 8, 16, 25, 33,</acronym> your armour by <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Constitution 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">2, 7, 14, 21, 28,</acronym> your armour hardiness by 20% and your saves by <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Constitution 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">3, 8, 16, 25, 33</acronym> as your natural toughness and reflexes are pushed beyond their normal limits.</p><p>Your saves armour and defense will improve with your Constitution.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Corrupted Shell","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Con 50; Have received at least 3500 blight damage and destroyed Zigur with the Grand Corruptor."],"short_name":"CORRUPTED_SHELL","source_code":["data/talents/uber/const.lua",175],"type":["uber/constitution",1],"uber":true},{"cooldown":12,"id":"T_SUBCUTANEOUS_METALLISATION","image":"subcutaneous_metallisation.png","info_text":"<p>When your life dips below 50% of your total life an automated process turns some of your lower skin layers (or other internal organs) into a thick metallic layer for 6 turns.</p><p>While the effect lasts all damage done to you is reduced by a flat amount equal to 100% of your Constitution.</p><p>This effect can only trigger once every 12 turns.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Subcutaneous Metallisation","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Con 50, Talent Thick Skin (5)"],"short_name":"SUBCUTANEOUS_METALLISATION","source_code":["data-orcs/talents/uber/const.lua",20],"type":["uber/constitution",1],"uber":true}],"type":"uber/constitution"},{"__ATOMIC":true,"category":"uber","description":"Ultimate talents you may only know one.","hide":true,"name":"cunning","points":1,"source":"@vanilla@","talents":[{"id":"T_FAST_AS_LIGHTNING","image":"fast_as_lightning.png","info_text":"<p>When moving over 800% speed for at least 3 steps in the same direction, you become so fast you can blink through obstacles as if they were not there.</p><p>While moving this fast you have 50% chances to fully ignore an attack by displacing yourself (this may only happen once per turn).</p><p>Changing direction will break the effect.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Fast As Lightning","not_listed":true,"points":1,"require":["Level 25, Cun 50"],"short_name":"FAST_AS_LIGHTNING","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/uber/cun.lua",20],"type":["uber/cunning",1],"uber":true},{"id":"T_TRICKY_DEFENSES","image":"tricky_defenses.png","info_text":"<p>You are full of tricks and surprises; your Antimagic Shield can absorb <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Cunning 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">10%, 20%, 32%, 42%, 50%</acronym> more damage.</p><p>The increase scales with your Cunning.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Tricky Defenses","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Cun 50; Antimagic"],"short_name":"TRICKY_DEFENSES","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/uber/cun.lua",72],"type":["uber/cunning",1],"uber":true},{"dts":{"ACID":true,"BLIGHT":true,"DARKNESS":true,"MIND":true,"PHYSICAL":true,"TEMPORAL":true},"id":"T_ENDLESS_WOES","image":"endless_woes.png","info_text":"<p>Surround yourself with a malevolent aura that stores damage you deal.</p><p>Whenever you have stored <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Cunning 10, 25, 50, 75, 100,<br>character level 1, 10, 25, 40, 50\\">16, 160, 400, 640, 800</acronym> damage of one type you unleash a powerful blast at a random enemy dealing <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Cunning 10, 25, 50, 75, 100,<br>character level 1, 10, 25, 40, 50\\">10, 101, 204, 283, 350</acronym> damage of that type in radius 3 and applying one of the following effects:</p><p></p><p>Physical:\\t\\tSlows combat, mind, and spell speed by 20%.</p><p><span style=\\"color: #008645\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-GREEN\\">Acid:</span></span>  Deals <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Cunning 10, 25, 50, 75, 100,<br>character level 1, 10, 25, 40, 50\\">10, 29, 55, 78, 99</acronym> acid damage each turn for 5 turns (<acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Cunning 10, 25, 50, 75, 100,<br>character level 1, 10, 25, 40, 50\\">50, 146, 278, 393, 499</acronym> total).</p><p><span style=\\"color: #324d0c\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-DARK_GREEN\\">Blight:</span></span>  Deals <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Cunning 10, 25, 50, 75, 100,<br>character level 1, 10, 25, 40, 50\\">1, 5, 10, 15, 20</acronym> blight damage each turn for 5 turns and reduces strength, constitution, and dexterity by <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Cunning 10, 25, 50, 75, 100,<br>character level 1, 10, 25, 40, 50\\">5, 10, 17, 24, 30.</acronym></p><p><span style=\\"color: #7f7f7f\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-GREY\\">Darkness:</span></span>  Reduces damage dealt by <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Cunning 10, 25, 50, 75, 100,<br>character level 1, 10, 25, 40, 50\\">1%, 7%, 15%, 23%, 30%</acronym> for 5 turns.</p><p><span style=\\"color: #b0c4de\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-LIGHT_STEEL_BLUE\\">Temporal:</span></span>  Slows global action speed by <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Cunning 10, 25, 50, 75, 100,<br>character level 1, 10, 25, 40, 50\\">1%, 9%, 20%, 30%, 40%</acronym> for 5 turns.</p><p><span style=\\"color: #ff7700\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-ORANGE\\">Mind:</span></span>  Confuses (power <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Cunning 10, 25, 50, 75, 100,<br>character level 1, 10, 25, 40, 50\\">1%, 9%, 20%, 30%, 40%</acronym>) for 5 turns.</p><p></p><p>Each effect can only happen once per 10 player turns.  This does not count as a typical cooldown.</p><p>The damage and effect power increase with your Cunning, the threshold with your level, and the apply power is the highest of your mind or spell power.</p><p></p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Endless Woes","points":1,"radius":3,"range":10,"require":["Level 25, Cun 50; Have dealt over 10000 acid, blight, darkness, mind or temporal damage"],"short_name":"ENDLESS_WOES","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/uber/cun.lua",85],"type":["uber/cunning",1],"uber":true},{"cant_steal":true,"id":"T_SECRETS_OF_TELOS","image":"secrets_of_telos.png","info_text":"<p>You have obtained the three parts of the Staff of Telos and studied them carefully. You believe that you can merge them back into a single highly potent staff.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Secrets of Telos","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Cun 50; Possess Telos Top Half, Telos Bottom Half, and Telos Staff Crystal"],"short_name":"SECRETS_OF_TELOS","source_code":["data/talents/uber/cun.lua",210],"type":["uber/cunning",1],"uber":true},{"dts":{"ARCANE":true,"COLD":true,"FIRE":true,"LIGHT":true,"LIGHTNING":true,"NATURE":true,"PHYSICAL":true},"id":"T_ELEMENTAL_SURGE","image":"elemental_surge.png","info_text":"<p>Surround yourself with an elemental aura that stores damage you deal.</p><p>Whenever you have stored <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Cunning 10, 25, 50, 75, 100,<br>character level 1, 10, 25, 40, 50\\">16, 160, 400, 640, 800</acronym> damage of one type you unleash a powerful blast at a random enemy dealing <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Cunning 10, 25, 50, 75, 100,<br>character level 1, 10, 25, 40, 50\\">10, 101, 204, 283, 350</acronym> damage of that type in radius 3 and granting you one of the following effects:</p><p></p><p>Physical:\\t\\tCleanses 1 physical debuff and grant immunity to physical debuffs for 2 turns.</p><p><span style=\\"color: #80008b\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-PURPLE\\">Arcane:</span></span>\\t\\tIncreases your mind and spell action speeds by 30% for 3 turns.</p><p><span style=\\"color: #ff0068\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-LIGHT_RED\\">Fire:</span></span>\\t\\tIncreases all damage dealt by 30% for 3 turns.</p><p><span style=\\"color: #1133F3\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-1133F3\\">Cold:</span></span>\\t\\tTurns your skin into ice for 3 turns increasing armor by <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Cunning 10, 25, 50, 75, 100,<br>character level 1, 10, 25, 40, 50\\">10, 14, 20, 25, 30</acronym> and dealing 100 ice damage to attackers.</p><p><span style=\\"color: #006cff\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-ROYAL_BLUE\\">Lightning:</span></span>\\tIncreases your movement speed by <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Cunning 10, 25, 50, 75, 100,<br>character level 1, 10, 25, 40, 50\\">200%, 264%, 352%, 429%, 500%</acronym> for 2 turns.</p><p><span style=\\"color: #ffff00\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-YELLOW\\">Light:</span></span>\\t\\tReduces all cooldowns by 20% for 3 turns.</p><p><span style=\\"color: #00ff00\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-LIGHT_GREEN\\">Nature:</span></span>\\t\\tCleanses 1 magical debuff and grant immunity to magical debuffs for 2 turns.</p><p></p><p>Each effect can only happen once per 10 player turns.  This does not count as a typical cooldown.</p><p>The damage and some effect powers increase with your Cunning and the threshold with your level.</p><p></p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Elemental Surge","points":1,"radius":3,"range":10,"require":["Level 25, Cun 50; Have dealt over 10000 arcane, fire, cold, lightning, light or nature damage"],"short_name":"ELEMENTAL_SURGE","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/uber/cun.lua",247],"type":["uber/cunning",1],"uber":true},{"id":"T_EYE_OF_THE_TIGER","image":"eye_of_the_tiger.png","info_text":"<p>All spell criticals reduce the remaining cooldown of a random spell/corruption/celestial/chronomancy talent by 2.</p><p>All physical criticals reduce the remaining cooldown of a random technique or cunning talent by 2.</p><p>All mind criticals reduce the remaining cooldown of a random wild gift/psionic/afflicted talent by 2.</p><p>All steamtech criticals reduce the remaining cooldown of a random steamtech talent by 1.\\t\\t</p><p>This can only happen once per turn per type, and cannot affect the talent that triggers it.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Eye of the Tiger","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Cun 50"],"short_name":"EYE_OF_THE_TIGER","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/uber/cun.lua",390],"type":["uber/cunning",1],"uber":true},{"cant_steal":true,"id":"T_WORLDLY_KNOWLEDGE","image":"worldly_knowledge.png","info_text":"<p>Gain 5 generic talent points and learn a new talent category from one of the below at 1.0 mastery, unlocked. Group 1 categories are available to anyone; Group 2 are not available to magic users, and Group 3 are not available to antimagic characters.</p><p>GROUP 1:</p><ul><li> Cunning / Scoundrel</li><li> Cunning / Survival</li><li> Technique / Conditioning</li></ul><p></p><p>GROUP 2:</p><ul><li> Psionic / Augmented mobility</li><li> Psionic / Dreaming</li><li> Psionic / Feedback</li><li> Wild-gift / Call of the wild</li><li> Wild-gift / Mindstar mastery</li></ul><p></p><p>GROUP 3:</p><ul><li> Celestial / Chants</li><li> Chronomancy / Chronomancy</li><li> Corruption / Curses</li><li> Spell / Divination</li><li> Spell / Staff combat</li><li> Spell / Stone alchemy</li></ul><p></p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Worldly Knowledge","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Cun 50"],"short_name":"WORLDLY_KNOWLEDGE","source_code":["data/talents/uber/cun.lua",429],"type":["uber/cunning",1],"uber":true},{"cant_steal":true,"id":"T_ADEPT","image":"adept.png","info_text":"<p>You are adept at many different skills, granting you +1.5 to all known talent levels.</p><p>This works on already known talents and those that you will learn afterwards.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Adept","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Cun 50"],"short_name":"ADEPT","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/uber/cun.lua",499],"type":["uber/cunning",1],"uber":true},{"cant_steal":true,"id":"T_TRICKS_OF_THE_TRADE","image":"tricks_of_the_trade.png","info_text":"<p>You have friends in low places and have learned some underhanded tricks.</p><p>Gain 0.2 Category Mastery to the Cunning/Stealth Category (or unlock it, if you have the tree and it is locked), and either gain +0.1 to the Cunning/Scoundrel category or learn and unlock the category at 0.9 if you lack it.</p><p>Additionally, all of your damage penalties from invisibility are permanently halved.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Tricks of the Trade","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Cun 50; Have sided with the Assassin Lord"],"short_name":"TRICKS_OF_THE_TRADE","source_code":["data/talents/uber/cun.lua",513],"type":["uber/cunning",1],"uber":true},{"id":"T_MASTER_OF_DISASTERS","image":"master_of_disasters.png","info_text":"<p>You are adept at wreaking havoc onto your foes!</p><p>Any time you deal damage to a creature you apply the Incoming Disasters effect for 20 turns.</p><p>Each time you (or any others) would try to apply a cross-tier effect to this creature, you also try to apply the other two.</p><p>In addition your physical, steam, spell and mind powers are increased by <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Cunning 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">26, 35, 50, 65, 80.</acronym></p><p>The powers increase scales of your Cunning.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Master of Disasters","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Cun 50"],"short_name":"MASTER_OF_DISASTERS","source_code":["1.7.4/data-orcs/talents/uber/cun.lua",22],"type":["uber/cunning",1],"uber":true},{"cant_steal":true,"id":"T_RAKSHOR_CUNNING","image":"rakshor_cunning.png","info_text":"<p>Set up some cunning contingency plans in case of death.</p><p>If you die you will have the option to raise back from the dead once, by becoming a ghoul or a skeleton (you can choose which).</p><p>When rising this way you will keep access to your racial tree and gain access to the ghoul or skeleton racial tree with 2 levels of each talents already learnt.</p><p>As undead will not able to use infusions anymore.</p><p>If you choose to become a skeleton, the Re-assemble talent will consider that you already used your resurrection.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"#SANDY_BROWN#Rak\'Shor\'s Cunning (Race Evolution)","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Cun 50; Quaffed the Blood of Undeath, not already undead and not antimagic."],"short_name":"RAKSHOR_CUNNING","source_code":["data-orcs/talents/uber/cun.lua",46],"type":["uber/cunning",1],"uber":true}],"type":"uber/cunning"},{"__ATOMIC":true,"category":"uber","description":"Ultimate talents you may only know one.","hide":true,"name":"dexterity","points":1,"source":"@vanilla@","talents":[{"id":"T_FLEXIBLE_COMBAT","image":"flexible_combat.png","info_text":"<p>Each time that you make a melee attack you have a 50% chance to execute an additional unarmed strike.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Flexible Combat","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Dex 50"],"short_name":"FLEXIBLE_COMBAT","source_code":["data/talents/uber/dex.lua",20],"type":["uber/dexterity",1],"uber":true},{"id":"T_THROUGH_THE_CROWD","image":"through_the_crowd.png","info_text":"<p>You are used to a crowded party:</p><ul><li> you can swap places with friendly creatures in just one tenth of a turn as a passive effect.</li><li> you can never damage your friends or neutral creatures while this talent is active.</li><li> you love being surrounded by friends; for each friendly creature in sight you gain +10 to all saves and +3% to global speed (max 15%)</li><li> every party member is also automatically granted Through The Crowd</li></ul>","mode":"sustained","multi_require":false,"name":"Through The Crowd","points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 25, Dex 50; Have had at least 6 party members at the same time"],"short_name":"THROUGH_THE_CROWD","source_code":["data/talents/uber/dex.lua",37],"type":["uber/dexterity",1],"uber":true,"use_speed":"Standard"},{"autolearn_talent":"T_SWIFT_HANDS_EQUIP","cant_steal":true,"cooldown":3,"fixed_cooldown":true,"id":"T_SWIFT_HANDS","image":"swift_hands.png","info_text":"<p>You like to keep your most precious tools always at hand. This talent lets you prepare up to 4 items in advance (outside of combat).</p><p>Then at a moment\'s notice you can use any of them as if they were worn.</p><p>In addition swapping equipment sets (default q key) takes no time.</p>","mode":"activated","multi_require":false,"name":"Swift Hands","no_energy":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 25, Dex 50"],"short_name":"SWIFT_HANDS","source_code":["data/talents/uber/dex.lua",112],"type":["uber/dexterity",1],"uber":true,"use_speed":"Instant"},{"cooldown":12,"id":"T_WINDBLADE","image":"windblade.png","info_text":"<p>You spin madly, generating a sharp gust of wind with your weapons that deals 320% weapon damage to all targets within radius 4 and disarms them for 4 turns.</p>","is_melee":true,"mode":"activated","multi_require":false,"name":"Windblade","points":1,"radius":4,"range":"0.0","require":["Level 25, Dex 50; Have dealt over 50000 damage with dual wielded weapons"],"requires_target":true,"short_name":"WINDBLADE","source_code":["data/talents/uber/dex.lua",155],"type":["uber/dexterity",1],"uber":true,"use_speed":"Weapon"},{"id":"T_WINDTOUCHED_SPEED","image":"windtouched_speed.png","info_text":"<p>You are attuned with Nature, and she helps you in your fight against the arcane forces.</p><p>You gain 20% permanent global speed, 10% cooldowns reduction and do not trigger pressure traps.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Windtouched Speed","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Dex 50; Know at least 10 talent levels of equilibrium-using talents"],"short_name":"WINDTOUCHED_SPEED","source_code":["data/talents/uber/dex.lua",189],"type":["uber/dexterity",1],"uber":true},{"cant_steal":true,"id":"T_CRAFTY_HANDS","image":"crafty_hands.png","info_text":"<p>You are very crafty. You can now also embed gems into helms and belts.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Crafty Hands","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Dex 50; Know Imbue Item to level 5"],"short_name":"CRAFTY_HANDS","source_code":["data/talents/uber/dex.lua",212],"type":["uber/dexterity",1],"uber":true},{"cooldown":10,"id":"T_ROLL_WITH_IT","image":"roll_with_it.png","info_text":"<p>You have learned to take a few hits when needed and can flow with the tide of battle.</p><p>So long as you can move, you find a way to dodge, evade, deflect or otherwise reduce physical damage against you by <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Dexterity 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">3%, 6%, 9%, 12%, 15%.</acronym></p><p>Once per turn, when you get hit by a melee or archery attack you move back one tile for free and gain 200% movement speed for a turn.</p><p>The damage avoidance scales with your Dexterity and applies after resistances.</p>","mode":"sustained","multi_require":false,"name":"Roll With It","points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 25, Dex 50; Have been knocked around at least 50 times"],"short_name":"ROLL_WITH_IT","source_code":["data/talents/uber/dex.lua",226],"type":["uber/dexterity",1],"uber":true,"use_speed":"Standard"},{"cooldown":10,"id":"T_VITAL_SHOT","image":"vital_shot.png","info_text":"<p>You fire a shot straight at your enemy\'s vital areas, wounding them terribly.</p><p>Enemies hit by this shot will take 450% weapon damage and will be stunned and crippled (losing 50% physical, magical and mental attack speeds) for five turns due to the devastating impact of the shot.</p><p>The stun and cripple chances increase with your Accuracy.</p>","mode":"activated","multi_require":false,"name":"Vital Shot","no_energy":"fake","points":1,"range":"archery","require":["Level 25, Dex 50; Have dealt over 50000 damage with ranged weapons"],"requires_target":true,"short_name":"VITAL_SHOT","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/uber/dex.lua",256],"type":["uber/dexterity",1],"uber":true,"use_speed":"Standard"},{"cooldown":4,"id":"T_AUTOMATED_REFLEX_SYSTEM","image":"automated_reflex_system.png","info_text":"<p>A small automatic detection system is always looking for incoming projectiles, when one is about to hit you it injects drugs into your system to boost your reactivity, granting you a free turn.</p><p>This effect can not happen more than once every 5 turns.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Automated Reflex System","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Dex 50; Have gained the <span style=\\"font-style: italic\\"><span class=\\"tstr-font-italic\\">Matrix Style</span></span> achievement with this or any previous character for the current difficulty & permadeath settings."],"short_name":"AUTOMATED_REFLEX_SYSTEM","source_code":["1.7.4/data-orcs/talents/uber/dex.lua",20],"type":["uber/dexterity",1],"uber":true}],"type":"uber/dexterity"},{"__ATOMIC":true,"category":"uber","description":"Ultimate talents you may only know one.","hide":true,"name":"magic","points":1,"source":"@vanilla@","talents":[{"id":"T_SPECTRAL_SHIELD","image":"spectral_shield.png","info_text":"<p>By infusing your shield with raw magic, your block can now block any damage type.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Spectral Shield","not_listed":true,"points":1,"require":["Level 25, Mag 50; Know the Block talent, have cast 100 spells, and have a block value over 200"],"short_name":"SPECTRAL_SHIELD","source_code":["data/talents/uber/mag.lua",22],"type":["uber/magic",1],"uber":true},{"id":"T_ETHEREAL_FORM","image":"displace_damage.png","info_text":"<p>You gain 25% absolute damage resistance and 25% all damage penetration.  Each time you are struck by a weapon these bonuses are reduced by 5% but fully recovered after 8 turns.</p><p>Additionally, you gain 70% of the highest of your Magic or Dexterity stat as defense (<acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Dexterity 10, 25, 50, 75, 100,<br>Magic 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">7, 17, 35, 52, 70</acronym>)</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Ethereal Form","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Mag 50; Have an effective defense of at least 40"],"short_name":"ETHEREAL_FORM","source_code":["data/talents/uber/mag.lua",42],"type":["uber/magic",1],"uber":true},{"callbackPriorities":{"callbackOnDispel":-9999},"cooldown":20,"id":"T_AETHER_PERMEATION","image":"aether_permeation.png","info_text":"<p>You manifest a thin layer of aether all around you. </p><p>Any time you are the target of a dispel effect the aether strengthens around you, protecting you from the dispel and any further ones for 6 turns and unsustaining this spell.</p><p>While undisturbed the layer of aether provides you with 40 raw spellpower.</p>","mode":"sustained","multi_require":false,"name":"Aether Permeation","points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 25, Mag 50; Have been exposed to the void of space"],"short_name":"AETHER_PERMEATION","source_code":["",71],"type":["uber/magic",1],"uber":true,"use_speed":"Standard"},{"autolearn_talent":["T_VULNERABILITY_POISON","T_GRAVITIC_TRAP"],"id":"T_MYSTICAL_CUNNING","image":"vulnerability_poison.png","info_text":"<p>Your study of arcane forces has let you develop a new way of applying your aptitude for trapping and poisons.</p><p></p><p>You gain 1.0 mastery in the Cunning/Poisons and Cunning/Trapping talent trees.</p><p>Your Venomous Strike talent cooldown is reduced by 3.</p><p>Your Lure talent cooldown is reduced by 5.</p><p></p><p>You learn the following talents:</p><p></p><p><span style=\\"color: #ffff00\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-YELLOW\\">Vulnerability Poison</span></span></p><p>Whenever you apply Deadly Poison, you also apply an unresistable magical poison dealing <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Magic 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">20, 26, 35, 43, 50</acronym> arcane damage (based on your Magic) each turn. This poison reduces all damage resistance by 10% and poison immunity by 50%.</p><p></p><p><span style=\\"color: #ffff00\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-YELLOW\\">Gravitic Trap</span></span></p><p>Lay a trap that creates a radius 5 gravitic anomaly when triggered by foes approaching within range 1.  Each turn, the anomaly deals <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Magic 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">20, 31, 43, 52, 60</acronym> temporal damage (based on your Magic) to foes while pulling them towards its center (chance increases with your combat accuracy or spell power, whichever is higher).</p><p>Each anomaly lasts 2 turns (up to the amount of time since the last anomaly dissipated, based on your Trap Mastery skill).</p><p>The trap may trigger more than once, but requires at least 2 turns to recharge between activations.</p><p>This design does not require advanced preparation to use.</p><p></p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Mystical Cunning","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Mag 50; Know how to either prepare traps or apply poisons"],"short_name":"MYSTICAL_CUNNING","source_code":["",103],"type":["uber/magic",1],"uber":true},{"id":"T_ARCANE_MIGHT","image":"arcane_might.png","info_text":"<p>You have learned to harness your latent arcane powers, channeling them through your weapon.</p><p>This has the following effects:</p><p>Equipped weapons are treated as having an additional 50% Magic modifier;</p><p>Your raw Physical Power is increased by 100% of your raw Spellpower;</p><p>Your physical critical chance is increased by 25% of your bonus spell critical chance.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Arcane Might","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Mag 50"],"short_name":"ARCANE_MIGHT","source_code":["data/talents/uber/mag.lua",136],"type":["uber/magic",1],"uber":true},{"cooldown":30,"id":"T_TEMPORAL_FORM","image":"temporal_form.png","info_text":"<p>You can wrap temporal threads around you, assuming the form of a telugoroth for 10 turns.</p><p>While in this form you gain pinning, bleeding, blindness and stun immunity, 30% temporal resistance, your temporal damage bonus is set to your current highest damage bonus + 30%, 50% of the damage you deal becomes temporal, and you gain 20% temporal resistance penetration.</p><p>You also are able to cast anomalies: Anomaly Rearrange, Anomaly Temporal Storm, Anomaly Flawed Design, Anomaly Gravity Pull and Anomaly Wormhole.</p>","is_spell":true,"mode":"activated","multi_require":false,"name":"Temporal Form","no_energy":true,"points":1,"range":"10.0","require":["Level 25, Mag 50; Have cast over 1000 spells and visited a zone outside of time"],"requires_target":true,"short_name":"TEMPORAL_FORM","source_code":["",149],"type":["uber/magic",1],"uber":true,"use_speed":"Instant"},{"cant_steal":true,"id":"T_BLIGHTED_SUMMONING","image":"blighted_summoning.png","info_text":"<p>You infuse blighted energies into all of your summons, granting them Bone Shield (level 3) and a bonus to Spellpower equal to your Magic.</p><p>Your Wilder Summons and Necrotic Minions will gain special corrupted talents (level 3), other summons will gain 10% Blight damage conversion and Virulent Disease (level 3).</p><p><span style=\\"color: #008645\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-GREEN\\">Wilder Summons:</span></span></p><ul><li> War Hound: Gnaw</li><li> Jelly: Curse of Defencelessness</li><li> Minotaur: Ruin</li><li> Golem: Acid Blood</li><li> Ritch: Life Tap</li><li> Hydra: Blood Spray</li><li> Rimebark: Poison Storm</li><li> Fire Drake: Flame of Urh’Rok</li><li> Turtle: Elemental Discord</li><li> Spider: Blood Grasp</li></ul><p><span style=\\"color: #7f7f7f\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-GREY\\">Necrotic Minions:</span></span></p><ul><li> Skeleton Mages: Bone Spear</li><li> Skeleton Archers: Bone Spike</li><li> Skeleton Warriors: Ruin</li><li> Bone Giants: Bone Spike and Ruin</li><li> Ghouls: Virulent Disease</li><li> Dread: Slumber</li></ul><p></p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Blighted Summoning","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Mag 50; Have summoned at least 100 creatures. More permanent summons may count as more than 1."],"short_name":"BLIGHTED_SUMMONING","source_code":["",172],"type":["uber/magic",1],"uber":true},{"cant_steal":true,"cooldown":30,"id":"T_REVISIONIST_HISTORY","image":"revisionist_history.png","info_text":"<p>You can now control the recent past. Upon using this prodigy you gain a temporal effect for 20 turns.</p><p>While this effect holds you can use the prodigy again to rewrite history.</p><p>This prodigy splits the timeline. Attempting to use another spell that also splits the timeline while this effect is active will be unsuccessful.</p>","is_spell":true,"mode":"activated","multi_require":false,"name":"Revisionist History","no_energy":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 25, Mag 50; Have time-travelled at least once"],"short_name":"REVISIONIST_HISTORY","source_code":["",279],"type":["uber/magic",1],"uber":true,"use_speed":"Instant"},{"cooldown":12,"id":"T_CAUTERIZE","image":"cauterize.png","info_text":"<p>Your inner flame is strong. Each time that you receive a blow that would kill you, your body is wreathed in flames.</p><p>The flames will cauterize the wound, fully absorbing all damage done this turn, but they will continue to burn for 8 turns.</p><p>Each turn 10% of the damage absorbed will be dealt by the flames. This will bypass resistance and affinity.</p><p>Warning: this has a cooldown.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Cauterize","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Mag 50; Have received at least 3500 fire damage and have cast at least 1000 spells"],"short_name":"CAUTERIZE","source_code":["data/talents/uber/mag.lua",330],"type":["uber/magic",1],"uber":true},{"cant_steal":true,"id":"T_LICH","image":"lich.png","info_text":"<p>This is your true goal and the purpose of all necromancy - to become a powerful and everliving Lich!</p><p>Once learnt, the next time you are killed, the arcane forces you unleash will be able to rebuild your body into the desired Lichform.</p><p>Liches are immune to poisons, diseases, fear, cuts, stuns, do not need to breath and are 20% resistant to cold and darkness.</p><p>Liches also gain +12 Magic, Willpower and Cunning, 60% chance to ignore critical hits, +4 life rating (not retroactive), +35 spell and mental saves and 7 mana regeneration.</p><p></p><p>Liches gain a new racial tree with the following talents:</p><ul><li> Neverending Unlife: A Lich body is extremely resilient, being able to go into negative life and when destroyed it can regenerate itself.</li><li> Frightening Presence: Your mere presence is enough to shatter the resolve of most, reducing their saves, damage and movement speed.</li><li> Doomed for Eternity: As a creature of doom and despair you now constantly spawn undead shadows around you.</li><li> Commander of the Dead: You are able to infuse all undead party members (including yourself) with un-natural power, increasing your physical and spellpower.</li></ul><p></p>","is_necromancy":true,"is_spell":true,"mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"#SANDY_BROWN#Lich (Race Evolution)","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Wil 25, Mag 50; Is a living creature that knows necromancy"],"short_name":"LICH","source_code":["",352],"type":["uber/magic",1],"uber":true},{"cant_steal":true,"id":"T_HIGH_THAUMATURGIST","image":"high_thaumaturgist.png","info_text":"<p>Thaumaturgists have unlocked a deeper understanding of their spells, allowing them to combine the elements into new ways and to empower them.</p><p>The spells Flame, Manathrust, Lightning, Pulverizing Auger and Ice Shards are permanently turned into 3-wide beams spells.</p><p>In addition they have access to the unique Thaumaturgy class tree:</p><ul><li> Orb of Thaumaturgy: a temporary orb that duplicates any beam spells that you cast</li><li> Multicaster: When casting a beam spell adds a chance to also cast an other archmage spell</li><li> Slipstream: Allows movement when casting beams</li><li> Elemental Array Burst: a powerful, multi-elemental beam spell that can inflict all elemental ailments and can not be resisted</li></ul><p><span style=\\"color: #dc143c\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-CRIMSON\\">The fine spellcasting required for wide beams and all thaumaturgy spells can only happen while wearing cloth. Anything heavier will hinder the casting too much.</p>","is_class_evolution":"Archmage","is_spell":true,"mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"#LIGHT_STEEL_BLUE#High Thaumaturgist (Class Evolution)","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Wil 25, Mag 50; Unlocked the High Thaumaturgist evolution"],"requires_unlock":"mage_thaumaturgist","short_name":"HIGH_THAUMATURGIST","source_code":["data/talents/uber/mag.lua",470],"type":["uber/magic",1],"uber":true},{"cooldown":10,"id":"T_ARCANE_AMPLIFICATION_DRONE","image":"arcane_amplification_drone.png","info_text":"<p>You create an Arcane Amplification Drone at the selected location for 3 turns.</p><p>When you cast a spell that damages the drone it will ripple the damage as 130% arcane damage of the initial hit in radius 4.</p>","mode":"activated","multi_require":false,"name":"Arcane Amplification Drone","no_energy":true,"points":1,"range":"7.0","require":["Level 25, Mag 50; Have gained the <span style=\\"font-style: italic\\"><span class=\\"tstr-font-italic\\">Tales of the Spellblaze</span></span> achievement with this or any previous character for the current difficulty & permadeath settings."],"short_name":"ARCANE_AMPLIFICATION_DRONE","source_code":["data-orcs/talents/uber/mag.lua",45],"type":["uber/magic",1],"uber":true,"use_speed":"Instant"},{"cant_steal":true,"id":"T_TECHNOMANCER","image":"technomancer.png","info_text":"<p>Technomancers are Archmages that dabble in steam technology to enhance their already formidable arsenal of spells.</p><p>Once this class evolution is taken, you gain the following:</p><ul><li> Arcane Dynamo tinker schematic</li><li> Steamtech/Physics category (unlocked)</li><li> Steamtech/Chemistry category (locked)</li><li> An Automated Portable Extractor (A.P.E.)</li><li> One point in the Physics talent Smith and two in Mechanical and Electricity</li><li> Spell/Galvanic Technomancy category (locked) - deals with fire and lightning</li><li> Spell/Terrene Technomancy category (locked) - deals with earth and water</li><li> Spell/Occult Technomancy category (locked) - deals with time and arcane</li><li> The ability to unlock one of the three Technomancy categories for free</li></ul><p></p><p>Once put in a robe, the Arcane Dynamo will regenerate Steam each time mana is spent and increase Spellpower based on current steam level.</p><p></p><p><span style=\\"font-weight: bold\\"><span class=\\"tstr-font-bold\\">As soon as this evolution is used you will need to craft the Arcane Dynamo to place in a robe to benefit from all the powers of the Technomancer.</span></span></p>","is_class_evolution":"Archmage","is_spell":true,"is_steam":true,"is_technomancy":true,"mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"#LIGHT_STEEL_BLUE#Technomancer (Class Evolution)","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Mag 50, Cun 25; Unlocked the Technomancer evolution"],"requires_unlock":"mage_technomancer","short_name":"TECHNOMANCER","source_code":["1.7.4/data-orcs/talents/uber/mag.lua",121],"type":["uber/magic",1],"uber":true}],"type":"uber/magic"},{"__ATOMIC":true,"category":"uber","description":"Ultimate talents you may only know one.","hide":true,"name":"other","points":1,"source":"@vanilla@","talents":[{"cooldown":30,"id":"T_REVISIONIST_HISTORY_BACK","image":"revisionist_history_back.png","info_text":"<p>Rewrite the recent past to go back to when you cast Revisionist History.</p>","is_spell":true,"mode":"activated","name":"Unfold History","no_energy":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","short_name":"REVISIONIST_HISTORY_BACK","source_code":["",309],"type":["uber/other",1],"use_speed":"Instant"}],"type":"uber/other"},{"__ATOMIC":true,"category":"uber","description":"Ultimate talents you may only know one.","hide":true,"name":"strength","points":1,"source":"@vanilla@","talents":[{"cooldown":20,"id":"T_GIANT_LEAP","image":"giant_leap.png","info_text":"<p>You accurately jump to the target and deal 200% weapon damage to all foes within radius 1 on impact as well as dazing them for 3 turns.</p><p>When you jump you free yourself from any stun, daze and pinning effects.</p>","is_melee":true,"mode":"activated","multi_require":false,"name":"Giant Leap","no_energy":true,"points":1,"radius":1,"range":"10.0","require":["Level 25, Str 50; Have dealt over 50000 damage with any weapon or unarmed"],"requires_target":true,"short_name":"GIANT_LEAP","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/uber/str.lua",20],"type":["uber/strength",1],"uber":true,"use_speed":"Instant"},{"cooldown":10,"id":"T_TITAN_S_SMASH","image":"titan_s_smash.png","info_text":"<p>You deal a massive blow to your foe, smashing it for 350% weapon damage, knocking it back 5 tiles, and knocking aside all foes in its path.</p><p>All targets affected are stunned for 3 turns.</p><p>For each size category over \'big\' you gain an additional +80% weapon damage.</p>","is_melee":true,"mode":"activated","multi_require":false,"name":"You Shall Be My Weapon!","points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 25, Str 50; Be of size category \'big\' or larger. This is also required to use it."],"requires_target":true,"short_name":"TITAN_S_SMASH","source_code":["data/talents/uber/str.lua",82],"type":["uber/strength",1],"uber":true,"use_speed":"Weapon"},{"cooldown":10,"id":"T_MASSIVE_BLOW","image":"massive_blow.png","info_text":"<p>You deal a massive blow to your foe, smashing it for 150% weapon damage and knocking it back 4 tiles (ignoring knockback resistance or physical save).</p><p>If the knockback makes it hit a wall, it will smash down the wall, deal an additional 350% weapon damage and apply the Counterstrike effect.</p>","is_melee":true,"mode":"activated","multi_require":false,"name":"Massive Blow","points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 25, Str 50; Have dug at least 30 walls/trees/etc. and have dealt over 50000 damage with two-handed weapons"],"requires_target":true,"short_name":"MASSIVE_BLOW","source_code":["data/talents/uber/str.lua",126],"type":["uber/strength",1],"uber":true,"use_speed":"Weapon"},{"id":"T_STEAMROLLER","image":"steamroller.png","info_text":"<p>When you rush, the creature you rush to is marked. If you kill it in the next two turns then your rush cooldown is reset.</p><p>Each time that this effect triggers you gain a stacking +20% damage buff, up to 100%.</p><p>Rush now only costs 2 stamina.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Steamroller","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Str 50; Know the Rush talent"],"short_name":"STEAMROLLER","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/uber/str.lua",164],"type":["uber/strength",1],"uber":true},{"cooldown":25,"id":"T_IRRESISTIBLE_SUN","image":"irresistible_sun.png","info_text":"<p>For 8 turns you gain the mass and power of a star, drawing all creatures within radius 5 toward you and dealing <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Strength 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">16, 23, 33, 44, 55</acronym> fire, <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Strength 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">16, 23, 33, 44, 55</acronym> light and <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Strength 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">16, 23, 33, 44, 55</acronym> physical damage to all foes and reducing their damage dealt by 30%.</p><p>Foes closer to you take up to 150% damage.</p><p>The damage will increase with your Strength.</p>","mode":"activated","multi_require":false,"name":"Irresistible Sun","points":1,"range":"5.0","require":["Level 25, Str 50; Have dealt over 50000 light or fire damage"],"requires_target":true,"short_name":"IRRESISTIBLE_SUN","source_code":["data/talents/uber/str.lua",176],"target":{"friendlyfire":false,"radius":5,"range":0,"type":"ball"},"type":["uber/strength",1],"uber":true,"use_speed":"Standard"},{"id":"T_NO_FATIGUE","image":"no_fatigue.png","info_text":"<p>Your strength is legendary; fatigue and physical exertion mean nothing to you.</p><p>Your fatigue is permanently set to 0, carrying capacity increased by 500, and strength increased by 50 and you gain a size category.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"I Can Carry The World!","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Str 50; Be able to use massive armours"],"short_name":"NO_FATIGUE","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/uber/str.lua",202],"type":["uber/strength",1],"uber":true},{"cant_steal":true,"id":"T_LEGACY_OF_THE_NALOREN","image":"legacy_of_the_naloren.png","info_text":"<p>You have sided with Slasul and helped him vanquish Ukllmswwik. You are now able to breathe underwater with ease.</p><p>You have also learned to use tridents and other exotic weapons easily (talent level <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>character level 1, 10, 25, 40, 50\\">1, 1, 3, 4, 5</acronym> of Exotic Weapon Mastery), and can Spit Poison (talent level <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>character level 1, 10, 25, 40, 50\\">1, 1, 3, 4, 5</acronym>) as nagas do. These are bonus talent levels that increase with your character level.</p><p>In addition, should Slasul still live, he may have a further reward for you as thanks&hellip;</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Legacy of the Naloren","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Str 50; Have sided with Slasul and killed Ukllmswwik"],"short_name":"LEGACY_OF_THE_NALOREN","source_code":["data/talents/uber/str.lua",223],"type":["uber/strength",1],"uber":true},{"id":"T_SUPERPOWER","image":"superpower.png","info_text":"<p>A strong body is key to a strong mind, and a strong mind can be powerful enough to make a strong body.</p><p>This prodigy grants a Mindpower bonus equal to 60% of your Strength.</p><p>Additionally, you treat all weapons as having an additional 40% Willpower modifier.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Superpower","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Str 50"],"short_name":"SUPERPOWER","source_code":["data/talents/uber/str.lua",269],"type":["uber/strength",1],"uber":true},{"cant_steal":true,"id":"T_AVATAR_OF_A_DISTANT_SUN","image":"avatar_of_a_distant_sun.png","info_text":"<p>During your studies of celestial forces you came in contact with an entity far beyond Eyal: the living incarnation of a Star!</p><p>By allying yourself with it you can gain its power!</p><p></p><p>Grants multiple benefits:</p><ul><li> The strength of your bond is so strong that you can now <span style=\\"color: #ffd700\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-GOLD\\">wield a two-handed weapon and a shield together</span></span></li><li> 50% of all damage you deal is converted to <span style=\\"color: #ffd700\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-GOLD\\">light damage</span></span></li><li> <span style=\\"color: #ffd700\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-GOLD\\">Gravitic Effulgence</span></span>: whenever your Weapon of Light hits the damage is now a radius 2 sphere and all foes in range 5 are drawn to it. (You can toggle this effect)</li><li> The damage and chance to trigger of <span style=\\"color: #ffd700\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-GOLD\\">Searing Sight</span></span> is doubled</li><li> Whenever <span style=\\"color: #ffd700\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-GOLD\\">Sun\'s Vengeance</span></span> triggers the remaining cooldown of Judgement is reduced by 6.</li><li> If you also know <span style=\\"color: #ffd700\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-GOLD\\">Irresistible Sun</span></span>, it will set the fire and light resistances of those affected to 0%</li></ul><p></p><p><span style=\\"font-style: italic\\"><span class=\\"tstr-font-italic\\"><span style=\\"color: #ffd700\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-GOLD\\">Will you bind yourself to the Distant Sun?</span></span></p><p></p>","is_class_evolution":"Sun Paladin","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"#LIGHT_STEEL_BLUE#Avatar of a Distant Sun (Class Evolution)","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Mag 25, Str 50; Unlocked the evolution, Talent Sun\'s Vengeance, Talent Weapon of Light, Talent Searing Sight, Talent Judgement"],"short_name":"AVATAR_OF_A_DISTANT_SUN","source_code":["data/talents/uber/str.lua",281],"type":["uber/strength",1],"uber":true},{"cooldown":18,"id":"T_PAIN_ENHANCEMENT_SYSTEM","image":"pain_enhancement_system.png","info_text":"<p>When you deal a critical hit your embedded system activates, increasing all your primary stats except Strength by 50% of your Strength for 6 turns.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Pain Enhancement System","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Str 50; Earned the achievement \'Size Matters\' on this character."],"short_name":"PAIN_ENHANCEMENT_SYSTEM","source_code":["data-orcs/talents/uber/str.lua",20],"type":["uber/strength",1],"uber":true}],"type":"uber/strength"},{"__ATOMIC":true,"category":"uber","description":"Ultimate talents you may only know one.","hide":true,"name":"willpower","points":1,"source":"@vanilla@","talents":[{"cooldown":15,"fixed_cooldown":true,"id":"T_DRACONIC_WILL","image":"draconic_will.png","info_text":"<p>Your body is like that of a drake, easily resisting detrimental effects.</p><p>For 5 turns, no detrimental effects may target you.</p>","mode":"activated","multi_require":false,"name":"Draconic Will","no_energy":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 25, Wil 50; Be close to the draconic world"],"requires_target":true,"short_name":"DRACONIC_WILL","source_code":["data/talents/uber/wil.lua",20],"type":["uber/willpower",1],"uber":true,"use_speed":"Instant"},{"cooldown":15,"id":"T_METEORIC_CRASH","image":"meteoric_crash.png","info_text":"<p>When casting damaging spells or mind attacks, the release of your willpower can call forth a meteor to crash down near your foes.</p><p>The meteor deals <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>spellpower 10, 25, 50, 75, 100,<br>mindpower 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">50, 88, 150, 213, 275</acronym> fire and <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>spellpower 10, 25, 50, 75, 100,<br>mindpower 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">50, 88, 150, 213, 275</acronym> physical damage in radius 2 and stuns enemies for 3 turns.</p><p>Lava is created in radius 3 around the impact dealing <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>spellpower 10, 25, 50, 75, 100,<br>mindpower 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">40, 55, 80, 105, 130</acronym> fire damage per turn for 8 turns.  This will overwrite tiles that already have modified terrain.</p><p>You and your allies take no damage from either effect.</p><p></p><p>Additionally, your fire damage bonus and resistance penetration is set to your current highest damage bonus and resistance penetration. This applies to all fire damage you deal.</p><p>The damage scales with your Spellpower or Mindpower.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Meteoric Crash","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Wil 50; Have witnessed a meteoric crash"],"short_name":"METEORIC_CRASH","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/uber/wil.lua",39],"type":["uber/willpower",1],"uber":true},{"id":"T_GARKUL_S_REVENGE","image":"garkul_s_revenge.png","info_text":"<p>Garkul\'s spirit is with you. You now deal 1000% more damage to constructs and 20% more damage to humanoids and giants.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Garkul\'s Revenge","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Wil 50; Possess and wear two of Garkul\'s artifacts and know all about Garkul\'s life"],"short_name":"GARKUL_S_REVENGE","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/uber/wil.lua",147],"type":["uber/willpower",1],"uber":true},{"cooldown":15,"id":"T_HIDDEN_RESOURCES","image":"hidden_resources.png","info_text":"<p>You focus your mind on the task at hand, regardless of how dire the situation is.</p><p>For 5 turns, none of your talents use any resources.</p>","mode":"activated","multi_require":false,"name":"Hidden Resources","no_energy":true,"points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 25, Wil 50; Have been close to death(killed a foe while below 1 HP)"],"short_name":"HIDDEN_RESOURCES","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/uber/wil.lua",178],"type":["uber/willpower",1],"uber":true,"use_speed":"Instant"},{"id":"T_LUCKY_DAY","image":"lucky_day.png","info_text":"<p>Every day is your lucky day! You gain a permanent +40 luck bonus and 10% to move out of the way of every attack.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Lucky Day","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Wil 50; Be lucky already (at least +5 luck)"],"short_name":"LUCKY_DAY","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/uber/wil.lua",202],"type":["uber/willpower",1],"uber":true},{"cooldown":5,"id":"T_UNBREAKABLE_WILL","image":"unbreakable_will.png","info_text":"<p>Your will is so strong that you simply ignore mental effects used against you.</p><p>This effect can only occur once every 5 turns.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Unbreakable Will","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Wil 50"],"short_name":"UNBREAKABLE_WILL","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/uber/wil.lua",222],"type":["uber/willpower",1],"uber":true},{"cooldown":9,"id":"T_SPELL_FEEDBACK","image":"spell_feedback.png","info_text":"<p>Your will is a shield against assaults from crazed arcane users.</p><p>Each time that you take damage from a spell, you punish the spellcaster with <acronym class=\\"stat-variable\\" title=\\"Values for<br>Willpower 10, 25, 50, 75, 100\\">40, 70, 120, 170, 220</acronym> mind damage.</p><p>Also, they will suffer a 35% spell failure chance (with duration equal to the cooldown of the spell they used on you).</p><p>Note: this talent has a cooldown.</p>","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"Spell Feedback","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Wil 50; Antimagic"],"short_name":"SPELL_FEEDBACK","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/uber/wil.lua",238],"type":["uber/willpower",1],"uber":true},{"cooldown":20,"id":"T_MENTAL_TYRANNY","image":"mental_tyranny.png","info_text":"<p>Transcend the physical and rule over all with an iron will!</p><p>While this sustain is active, 33% of your damage is converted into mind damage.</p><p>Additionally, you gain +30% mind resistance penetration, and +10% mind damage.</p>","mode":"sustained","multi_require":false,"name":"Mental Tyranny","points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 25, Wil 50; Have dealt over 50000 mind damage"],"short_name":"MENTAL_TYRANNY","source_code":["1.7.4/data/talents/uber/wil.lua",263],"type":["uber/willpower",1],"uber":true,"use_speed":"Standard"},{"cant_steal":true,"id":"T_FALLEN","image":"fallen.png","info_text":"<p>The code of the Sun Paladins can be a heavy burden.\\t Wouldn\'t you like to let go?</p><p><span style=\\"font-style: italic\\"><span class=\\"tstr-font-italic\\"><span style=\\"color: #7f7f7f\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-GREY\\">To give in to the darkness?</span></span></span></span></p><p></p><p><span style=\\"color: #dc143c\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-CRIMSON\\">This evolution fundamentally alters your class and character in a huge way. Do not take it lightly.</span></span></p><p></p><p>Any offensive combat techniques or unlockable Celestial talent trees you know will be exchanged for cursed versions, allowing you to cut a bloody trail through enemies, turning your radiance to gloom, and more while also gaining new combat styles and defenses.</p><p></p><p>The following talent trees are swapped:</p><ul><li> <span style=\\"color: #ffd700\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-GOLD\\">Radiance</span></span> turns into <span style=\\"color: #dc143c\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-CRIMSON\\">Gloom</span></span>: Project onto others your own hate, hindering them</li><li> <span style=\\"color: #ffd700\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-GOLD\\">Guardian</span></span> turns into <span style=\\"color: #dc143c\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-CRIMSON\\">Crimson Templar</span></span>: Use the power of blood to control and defeat the fools that oppose you</li><li> <span style=\\"color: #ffd700\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-GOLD\\">Crusader</span></span> turns into <span style=\\"color: #dc143c\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-CRIMSON\\">Dark Sun</span></span>: Call upon the energies of dead suns to crush your foes</li></ul><p></p><p>You will learn the following talents trees:</p><ul><li> <span style=\\"color: #dc143c\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-CRIMSON\\">Bloodstained</span></span>: Make your foes bleed!</li><li> <span style=\\"color: #dc143c\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-CRIMSON\\">Darkside</span></span>: Every light casts a shadow, yours is powerful indeed</li><li> <span style=\\"color: #dc143c\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-CRIMSON\\">Hatred</span></span>: Manifest your hatred through bleeding</li><li> <span style=\\"color: #dc143c\\"><span class=\\"tstr-color-CRIMSON\\">Dirge</span></span>: Sing of death and sorrow to strengthen your resolve</li></ul><p></p><p>You will forget the following talent trees, refunding any talent points: Shield Offense, Two-handed Assault.</p><p>Also the cost of any talents of the Combat Techniques tree will be converted to hate instead of stamina.</p><p></p>","is_class_evolution":"Sun Paladin","mode":"passive","multi_require":false,"name":"#LIGHT_STEEL_BLUE#Fallen (Class Evolution)","points":1,"require":["Level 25, Mag 25, Wil 50; Unlocked the Fallen evolution"],"short_name":"FALLEN","source_code":["data/talents/uber/wil.lua",298],"type":["uber/willpower",1],"uber":true},{"cooldown":10,"id":"T_RANGE_AMPLIFICATION_DEVICE","image":"range_amplification_device.png","info_text":"<p>Activate a special focusing device that extends all your ranged spells and psionic powers range by 3 (only works on those with range 2 or more and up to 10 max).</p><p>The use of this device is very strenuous, increasing fatigue by 20% while active.</p>","mode":"sustained","multi_require":false,"name":"Range Amplification Device","points":1,"range":"melee/personal","require":["Level 25, Wil 50; Have a light radius of 10 or more"],"short_name":"RANGE_AMPLIFICATION_DEVICE","source_code":["1.7.4/data-orcs/talents/uber/wil.lua",20],"type":["uber/willpower",1],"uber":true,"use_speed":"Standard"}],"type":"uber/willpower"}]')}}]);